<h2><a class="anchor" name="_install_linux">
Linux Install</a></h2>
Installation of the library is very easy. Untar and unzip the source then type the following: <b>make</b> <b>BUILD=Release</b> <b>&amp;&amp;</b> <b>make</b> <b>install</b> <br>
<br>
 <b>NOTE:</b> Make sure you are logged in as root or a user that has access to system directories!<h2><a class="anchor" name="_install_windows">
Windows Install</a></h2>
Installation of the library is very easy. <ol>
<li>
Unpack sourse code on your machine </li>
<li>
Open the solution in the CSocket folder (CSocket.sln) </li>
<li>
Build library </li>
</ol>
